[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 0.8,
    "text": "Have a seat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 0.8,
    "endTime": 5.2,
    "text": "I know that noise is all because it's day nine of 12 Days of Giveaways."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.0,
    "endTime": 9.0,
    "text": "I know that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.665,
    "endTime": 11.29,
    "text": "We'll get to your gifts a little later."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.29,
    "endTime": 15.899999999999999,
    "text": "First, I want to talk about something that'll help you get through the stress of the holidays... liquor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.03,
    "endTime": 21.53,
    "text": "I'm kidding."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.53,
    "endTime": 23.36,
    "text": "I'm talking about reality TV."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.36,
    "endTime": 26.63,
    "text": "I think that they're starting to run out of ideas for shows."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.63,
    "endTime": 30.349,
    "text": "There are so many shows that get green-lit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.35,
    "endTime": 32.119,
    "text": "People like, yep, put that on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.119,
    "endTime": 38.2,
    "text": "I saw one, this is called Wrap Battle, and it's a competitive world of wrapping presents."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.2,
    "endTime": 47.150000000000006,
    "text": "And it gets about as dramatic as you'd think that it would, which is not at all, but boy, they try to make it dramatic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.15,
    "endTime": 49.47,
    "text": "Who turned off my hot glue gun?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.97,
    "endTime": 51.199999999999996,
    "text": "Who did that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.2,
    "endTime": 52.85,
    "text": "Uh-oh, sabotage."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.85,
    "endTime": 55.44,
    "text": "Seriously, somebody turned off my hot glue gun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.44,
    "endTime": 57.11,
    "text": "I want to know who did it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.11,
    "endTime": 58.519,
    "text": "I'm not joking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.52,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "I'm going to find out who did it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 61.422,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.422,
    "endTime": 65.5,
    "text": "If anybody in this room is going to turn off my hot glue gun, I think it would be Olga."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.503,
    "endTime": 67.67,
    "text": "I need to, I just want to tell you that it's not me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.67,
    "endTime": 70.28,
    "text": "I did not like the way you looked at me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.28,
    "endTime": 71.99,
    "text": "I did not sabotage no one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.99,
    "endTime": 73.49,
    "text": "I'm too busy for that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.49,
    "endTime": 76.339,
    "text": "Your reputation precedes you, and that is not on me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.34,
    "endTime": 77.33,
    "text": "Hey, stop it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.0,
    "endTime": 82.0,
    "text": "Sure, blame the Russians."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.85,
    "endTime": 84.835,
    "text": "Yeah, really, blame her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.835,
    "endTime": 86.96,
    "text": "Tune in next week to find out who gets a paper cut."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.96,
    "endTime": 89.21,
    "text": "It's really--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.21,
    "endTime": 91.74,
    "text": "Here's how I know when there are too many reality shows."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.74,
    "endTime": 93.365,
    "text": "They've just stopped trying to be real."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.365,
    "endTime": 101.69999999999999,
    "text": "This is called South Beach Tow and the acting on this \"reality\" show is unbelievable."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.7,
    "endTime": 103.22,
    "text": "I know what I got to do, ma'am."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.22,
    "endTime": 104.512,
    "text": "I'm here to repossess your car."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.512,
    "endTime": 105.218,
    "text": "Hey, Dave!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.218,
    "endTime": 106.61,
    "text": "Lift...."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.61,
    "endTime": 107.6,
    "text": "Which one is lift?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.6,
    "endTime": 108.89999999999999,
    "text": "You is not going nowhere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.9,
    "endTime": 110.93900000000001,
    "text": "You better get out of my way, and I'm not playing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.939,
    "endTime": 112.106,
    "text": "I'ma back up and I'll do it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.106,
    "endTime": 112.6,
    "text": "You ain't backing up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.6,
    "endTime": 113.91999999999999,
    "text": "Which one is lift?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.921,
    "endTime": 115.334,
    "text": "You ain't going nowhere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.334,
    "endTime": 116.276,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.0,
    "endTime": 119.7,
    "text": "Bernice!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.7,
    "endTime": 121.5,
    "text": "Oh, my God!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.5,
    "endTime": 122.0,
    "text": "Bernice!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.0,
    "endTime": 123.0,
    "text": "Oh, my God!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.484,
    "endTime": 126.505,
    "text": "God damn, I told her I was gonna back up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.505,
    "endTime": 127.63,
    "text": "What did you do to Bernice?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.63,
    "endTime": 129.00799999999998,
    "text": "It was an accident."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.008,
    "endTime": 129.758,
    "text": "We gotta go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.758,
    "endTime": 130.30100000000002,
    "text": "We gotta go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.301,
    "endTime": 130.801,
    "text": "Bernice!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.801,
    "endTime": 132.22,
    "text": "Oh, my God."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.22,
    "endTime": 135.01,
    "text": "Where are you going?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.01,
    "endTime": 135.82899999999998,
    "text": "Get back here!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.83,
    "endTime": 138.79000000000002,
    "text": "You killed my friend!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.79,
    "endTime": 142.0,
    "text": "I've never driven a tow truck before, but I can't let them get away."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.92,
    "endTime": 145.35899999999998,
    "text": "I've got you blocked in."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.36,
    "endTime": 146.68,
    "text": "Call an ambulance right away."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.68,
    "endTime": 148.51000000000002,
    "text": "I'm going to check on my friend."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.51,
    "endTime": 150.67,
    "text": "Bernice!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.67,
    "endTime": 151.70899999999997,
    "text": "I thought you were dead."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.07,
    "endTime": 163.76,
    "text": "I really could watch that 7,000 times."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.76,
    "endTime": 166.79999999999998,
    "text": "So they're doing something right, because it made me want to watch it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.8,
    "endTime": 170.17000000000002,
    "text": "This next one is a British show called Naked Attraction."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.17,
    "endTime": 175.7,
    "text": "Single people choose a date based on seeing someone from the head down naked."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.943,
    "endTime": 176.61,
    "text": "It's in Britain."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.61,
    "endTime": 180.5,
    "text": "It's completely uncensored, so you see everybody's crumpets."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.5,
    "endTime": 181.15,
    "text": "And--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.0,
    "endTime": 186.5,
    "text": "We have got six colored pods."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.56,
    "endTime": 195.3,
    "text": "Inside each and every one of them is a gorgeous young man, your Hollywood pinup, that is completely and utterly naked."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.39,
    "endTime": 197.72,
    "text": "Natural, muscley arms."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.72,
    "endTime": 200.195,
    "text": "A man's arms is-- it goes a long way, it really does."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.195,
    "endTime": 202.07,
    "text": "I know you're slightly obsessed with Titanic."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.07,
    "endTime": 202.57,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.57,
    "endTime": 210.6,
    "text": "So we are going to recreate the scene in Titanic where Kate Winslet is like that and Leo has got his arms around her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.6,
    "endTime": 214.03,
    "text": "So, anyone who could be your Jack?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.03,
    "endTime": 216.03,
    "text": "Maybe be we should try it with orange."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.03,
    "endTime": 217.66,
    "text": "OK, I'm going to move you this way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.66,
    "endTime": 218.299,
    "text": "Great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.3,
    "endTime": 220.19,
    "text": "Back into the pod."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.19,
    "endTime": 221.06,
    "text": "This is hilarious."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.06,
    "endTime": 223.07,
    "text": "Arms out like you're flying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.07,
    "endTime": 224.095,
    "text": "In you go, orange."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.0,
    "endTime": 228.0,
    "text": "Jack, I'm flying."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.0,
    "endTime": 233.6,
    "text": "Michelle, how did that feel?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.6,
    "endTime": 235.57,
    "text": "I did get a little touch of his hands."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.57,
    "endTime": 238.049,
    "text": "Nice, firm, manly hands, so that was nice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.0,
    "endTime": 244.9,
    "text": "Serious question-- are straight people OK?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.0,
    "endTime": 250.3,
    "text": "I'm concerned."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.96,
    "endTime": 254.8,
    "text": "Finally, there's a show somebody told me about called Extreme Love."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.8,
    "endTime": 256.88,
    "text": "It's about unexpected relationships."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.88,
    "endTime": 262.0,
    "text": "And I know I always say, if I have to see it then you have to see it, too, but I'm not sure you're going to want to see it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.0,
    "endTime": 264.95,
    "text": "So you can vote, OK?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.95,
    "endTime": 267.24,
    "text": "You have to know a couple of things ahead of time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.24,
    "endTime": 271.19,
    "text": "It's about a 31-year-old man dating a 91-year-old woman."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.19,
    "endTime": 272.42,
    "text": "Who wants to see it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.26,
    "endTime": 274.58,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.58,
    "endTime": 275.45,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.45,
    "endTime": 276.979,
    "text": "There's open-mouth kissing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.98,
    "endTime": 279.72200000000004,
    "text": "Still interested?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.722,
    "endTime": 281.64,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.64,
    "endTime": 283.26,
    "text": "It ends in a hotel room."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.26,
    "endTime": 283.844,
    "text": "Last chance."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.0,
    "endTime": 289.0,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 289.24,
    "endTime": 292.40000000000003,
    "text": "You're all sick."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.4,
    "endTime": 293.71,
    "text": "Here it is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.71,
    "endTime": 300.0,
    "text": "I enjoy sex, NASCAR and crochet, and a drink, occasionally."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.0,
    "endTime": 304.4,
    "text": "My older son is 71, and the youngest will be 50 in September."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.4,
    "endTime": 309.29999999999995,
    "text": "The fact that Margie's kids are old enough to be Kyle's parents didn't put him off."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.3,
    "endTime": 315.0,
    "text": "In fact, he was in hot pursuit of Marge from the moment they met."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.06,
    "endTime": 319.4,
    "text": "And when he finally got her in bed, Kyle was in for a steamy night."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.4,
    "endTime": 324.0,
    "text": "When I did the first time, I told a girlfriend where I was going to be."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 324.0,
    "endTime": 330.5,
    "text": "And then I called her when we were at the motel and said, guess who's tied up, and it's not me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 330.5,
    "endTime": 332.7,
    "text": "And he's laying on the bed hollering, help!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.7,
    "endTime": 333.2,
    "text": "Help!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 343.0,
    "endTime": 346.0,
    "text": "I am so, so sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 346.15,
    "endTime": 349.53,
    "text": "You have no one to blame but the people who raised their hands."
  }
]